'''俄羅斯－南奧塞梯關係'''，是指[[俄羅斯聯邦|俄羅斯聯邦]]和的[[南奧塞梯共和國|南奧塞梯共和國]]之間的雙邊關係。而南奧塞梯尚未被多數國家所承認<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.civil.ge/eng/article.php?id=15080 |title=Online Magazine - Civil Georgia |accessdate=2014-07-10 |archive-date=2007-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071008122452/http://www.civil.ge/eng/article.php?id=15080 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.crisisgroup.org/home/index.cfm?id=4887 |title=International Crisis Group - Georgia’s South Ossetia Conflict: Make Haste Slowl |accessdate=2014-07-10 |archive-date=2008-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080820170805/http://www.crisisgroup.org/home/index.cfm?id=4887 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Russia condemned for recognizing rebel regions">[http://edition.cnn.com/2008/WORLD/europe/08/26/russia.vote.georgia/index.html Russia condemned for recognizing rebel regions] {{Wayback|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2008/WORLD/europe/08/26/russia.vote.georgia/index.html |date=20140723204321 }}, CNN</ref>。

== 背景 ==
[[File:Dmitry_Medvedev_address_on_26_August_2008_regarding_Abkhazia_&_South_Ossetia.ogg|缩略图]][[德米特里·阿纳托利耶维奇·梅德韦杰夫|梅德韋傑夫]]於2008年宣佈承認南奧塞梯獨立的講話]]
2008年8月21日，於南奧塞梯有民眾舉行集會，呼籲時任[[俄羅斯總統|俄羅斯總統]][[德米特里·阿纳托利耶维奇·梅德韦杰夫|梅德韋傑夫]]和[[俄羅斯聯邦會議|俄羅斯聯邦會議]]正式承認南奧塞梯為獨立[[主權國家|主權國家]]<ref name="appeal">{{cite news|title=Abkhazia, S.Ossetia send sovereignty appeals to Russia|location=[[苏呼米|苏呼米]]|publisher=[[RIA_Novosti|RIA Novosti]]|date=2008-08-21|url=http://en.rian.ru/world/20080821/116198014.html|accessdate=2008-09-09|archive-date=2013-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130512094210/http://en.rian.ru/world/20080821/116198014.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Abkhazia sends request to Russia for recognition|location=[[苏呼米|苏呼米]]|publisher=[[RIA_Novosti|RIA Novosti]]|date=2008-08-21|url=http://en.rian.ru/russia/20080821/116189365.html|accessdate=2008-09-09|archive-date=2013-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130512103949/http://en.rian.ru/russia/20080821/116189365.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，同時[[南奧塞梯總統|南奧塞梯總統]][[愛德華·賈巴耶維奇·科科伊季|愛德華·賈巴耶維奇·科科伊季]]飛抵[[莫斯科|莫斯科]]，呼籲[[俄羅斯聯邦委員會|俄羅斯聯邦委員會]]承認其獨立；隨後，聯邦委員會於8月25日以後通過議案，呼籲梅德韋傑夫承認其與[[阿布哈茲|阿布哈茲]]的獨立並建交<ref name="fedcouncil">{{cite news|title=Russian upper house seeks independence for Georgian rebel regions|location=Moscow|publisher=RIA Novosti|date=2008-08-25|url=http://en.rian.ru/russia/20080825/116254039.html|accessdate=2008-09-09|archive-date=2013-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130512115026/http://en.rian.ru/russia/20080825/116254039.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Russia parliament asks president to recognise S.Ossetia, Abkhazia|location=[[Moscow|Moscow]]|publisher=[[RIA_Novosti|RIA Novosti]]|date=2008-08-25|url=http://en.rian.ru/russia/20080825/116264611.html|accessdate=2008-09-09|archive-date=2013-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130512110305/http://en.rian.ru/russia/20080825/116264611.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2008年，格魯吉亞軍隊侵入[[茨欣瓦利|茨欣瓦利]]引發[[2008年南奧塞梯戰爭|南奧塞梯戰爭]]，導致俄羅斯與格魯吉亞短暫的軍事衝突。8月26日，[[德米特里·阿纳托利耶维奇·梅德韦杰夫|梅德韋傑夫]]簽署總統令，承認阿布哈茲和南奧塞梯的獨立<ref>{{cite news|title=Russia recognises Georgia's breakaway republics -2|location=[[Moscow|Moscow]]|publisher=[[RIA_Novosti|RIA Novosti]]|date=2008-08-26|url=http://en.rian.ru/russia/20080826/116291407.html|accessdate=2008-09-09|archive-date=2013-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131002145146/http://en.rian.ru/russia/20080826/116291407.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] August 26, 2008: [http://www.nytimes.com/2008/08/27/world/europe/27russia.html?hp Russia Backs Independence of Georgian Enclaves] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/08/27/world/europe/27russia.html?hp |date=20140606234955 }} by [[Clifford_J._Levy|Clifford J. Levy]]</ref>；許多俄羅斯政府高層，包括時任[[俄羅斯總理|俄羅斯總理]][[普京|普京]]、副總理[[謝爾蓋·伊万諾夫|謝爾蓋·伊万諾夫]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://en.rian.ru/russia/20090208/120038987.html|title=Russia to stick to its decision on bases in S.Ossetia, Abkhazia|date=2009-02-08|publisher=[[RIA_Novosti|RIA Novosti]]|location=[[Munich|Munich]]|accessdate=2009-08-04|archive-date=2009-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090211172212/http://en.rian.ru/russia/20090208/120038987.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>、外交部部長[[謝爾蓋·拉夫羅夫|謝爾蓋·拉夫羅夫]]等人都表示支持此決定。[[歐盟|歐盟]]、[[美國|美國]]及[[北約|北約]]隨即譴責俄羅斯<ref name="rogozinnato">{{cite news|url=http://en.rian.ru/russia/20080827/116325556.html|title=Russia says recognition of S.Ossetia, Abkhazia irreversible|date=2008-08-27|publisher=[[RIA_Novosti|RIA Novosti]]|location=[[Brussels|Brussels]]|accessdate=2009-08-04|archive-date=2013-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130512104441/http://en.rian.ru/russia/20080827/116325556.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> ，又呼籲俄羅斯撤銷承認；[[格魯吉亞|格魯吉亞]]亦於2008年8月29日宣佈與俄羅斯斷交<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/08/29/world/europe/29iht-georgia.3.15746317.html|title=Georgia breaks off relations with Russia|date=2008-08-29|location=[[Tbilisi|Tbilisi]]|publisher=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|accessdate=2009-08-04|archive-date=2018-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180213135407/http://www.nytimes.com/2008/08/29/world/europe/29iht-georgia.3.15746317.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並宣稱南奧塞梯和阿布哈茲為被佔領土<ref name="sarkozypraise">{{cite news|url=http://en.rian.ru/world/20090808/155760058.html|title=Medvedev praises Sarkozy's role in S. Ossetia ceasefire|date=2009-08-08|publisher=[[RIA_Novosti|RIA Novosti]]|location=[[Moscow|Moscow]]|accessdate=2009-08-09|archive-date=2009-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090812041552/http://en.rian.ru/world/20090808/155760058.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 經濟關係 ==
由於南奧塞梯人口少，而且缺乏天然資源，因此其經濟完全依賴於俄羅斯的金融援助<ref name="russiaglobal">{{cite news|url=http://eng.globalaffairs.ru/numbers/26/1266.html|title=A Testing Ground for Modernization and a Showcase of Success|last=Delyagin|first=Mikhail|date=2009-03-08|publisher=Russia in Global Affairs|accessdate=2009-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090814072108/http://eng.globalaffairs.ru/numbers/26/1266.html|archive-date=2009-08-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2009年，俄羅斯根據早前達成的協議<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.regnum.ru/english/1131963.html|title=Russian government will conclude an agreement on financial aid with Abkhazia and South Ossetia|date=2009-03-02|publisher=REGNUM News Agency|accessdate=2009-08-05|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090718114729/http://www.regnum.ru/english/1131963.html|archivedate=2009-07-18}}</ref>撥出28億[[盧布|盧布]]，其後又額外撥出85億盧布，以協助南奧塞梯重建戰時被摧毀的房屋及社會設施<ref>{{cite news|url=http://en.rian.ru/russia/20090317/120599992.html|title=Russia signs financial aid deals with Abkhazia, South Ossetia-2|date=2009-03-17|location=[[Moscow|Moscow]]|publisher=[[RIA_Novosti|RIA Novosti]]|accessdate=2009-08-04|archive-date=2012-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121012191325/http://en.rian.ru/russia/20090317/120599992.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 軍事關係 ==
俄羅斯於2008年9月與南奧塞梯簽署了{{link-en|友誼、合作和互助協定|Agreement of Friendship, Cooperation, and Mutual Assistance}} ，保證如果南奧塞梯被攻擊，俄羅斯將會軍事干預<ref name="kremlintreaty">{{cite news|url=http://www.kremlin.ru/eng/speeches/2008/09/17/1948_type82912type82914type82915_206565.shtml|title=Statements following Signing of the Treaties on Friendship, Cooperation and Mutual Assistance with the Republics of Abkhazia and South Ossetia|date=2008-09-17|publisher=[[Presidential_Press_and_Information_Office|Presidential Press and Information Office]]|location=[[Moscow_Kremlin|The Kremlin]], [[Moscow|Moscow]]|accessdate=2009-08-04|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130417100306/http://www.kremlin.ru/eng/speeches/2008/09/17/1948_type82912type82914type82915_206565.shtml|archivedate=2013-04-17}}</ref><ref name="nytimestreaty">{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/09/17/world/europe/17iht-georgia.4.16247629.html|title=Russia signs pacts committing itself to defense of South Ossetia and Abkhazia|date=2008-09-17|location=[[Moscow|Moscow]]|publisher=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|accessdate=2009-08-04|archive-date=2019-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190628192627/https://www.nytimes.com/2008/09/17/world/europe/17iht-georgia.4.16247629.html}}</ref><ref name="riantreaty">{{cite news|url=http://en.rian.ru/world/20090120/119713656.html|title=Russia-S.Ossetia friendship treaty comes into force|date=2009-01-20|location=[[Moscow|Moscow]]|publisher=[[RIA_Novosti|RIA Novosti]]|accessdate=2009-08-04|archive-date=2009-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090210234758/http://en.rian.ru/world/20090120/119713656.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，又承諾於2008年11月派遣3700名[[軍人|軍人]]到南奧塞梯<ref>{{cite news|url=http://en.rian.ru/russia/20081119/118400373.html|title=Russia fully staffs bases in Abkhazia, S.Ossetia|date=2008-11-19|publisher=RIA Novosti|location=Moscow|accessdate=2009-08-05|archive-date=2013-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130501113517/http://en.rian.ru/russia/20081119/118400373.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，負責巡視與格魯吉亞的邊境地區<ref name="xinhuaborder">{{cite news|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2009-05/02/content_11301165.htm|title=S Ossetia confirms Russia monitoring its border with Georgia|date=2009-05-02|publisher=Xinhua News Agency|location=Moscow|accessdate=2009-08-08|archive-date=2009-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090505130157/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2009-05/02/content_11301165.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://en.rian.ru/russia/20090502/121414333.html|title=Russian guards take up duties on Abkhaz, S. Ossetia borders|date=2009-05-02|publisher=RIA Novosti|location=Rostov-on-Don|accessdate=2009-08-08|archive-date=2009-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090505073543/http://en.rian.ru/russia/20090502/121414333.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2009年6月，時任[[俄羅斯聯邦軍總參謀部部長|俄羅斯聯邦軍總參謀部部長]]{{link-en|尼古拉·馬卡羅夫|Nikolay Yegorovich Makarov}}指出將減少俄羅斯在南奧塞梯的軍力<ref>{{cite news|url=http://en.rian.ru/world/20090617/155274434.html|title=Russia to cut troops in Abkhazia, S.Ossetia — General Staff|date=2009-06-17|location=[[Le_Bourget|Le Bourget]], [[Paris|Paris]]|publisher=[[RIA_Novosti|RIA Novosti]]|accessdate=2009-08-05|archive-date=2009-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090620013351/http://en.rian.ru/world/20090617/155274434.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>；於2009年8月，時任南奧塞梯總統科科伊季接受採訪時表示俄羅斯不必於南奧塞梯駐軍，以緩解緊張局勢<ref name="kokoityrian">{{cite news|url=http://en.rian.ru/analysis/20090803/155710016.html|title=Eduard Kokoity: I rule out a new Georgian aggression|date=2009-08-03|publisher=[[RIA_Novosti|RIA Novosti]]|accessdate=2009-08-05|archive-date=2012-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121012190619/http://en.rian.ru/analysis/20090803/155710016.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

